To whom it may concern,

This is a written request, made pursuant to 15 U.S.C. §1692g(b), for
validation of the debt referenced above. Within 30 days of your first
written communication to me regarding this debt, you must:

  1. Provide verification of the debt, including the original creditor,
     the amount alleged, and an itemized statement;
  2. Cease all collection activity until validation is provided.

Until you have satisfied these obligations I do not waive any right
under the Fair Debt Collection Practices Act or the Fair Credit
Reporting Act, and I dispute the alleged debt in its entirety.

I prefer to be contacted only in writing at the address above. Do not
contact me by telephone.

Sincerely,


